project.name: PhpDaoGenerator
project.description: Data Access Object: design pattern, access to data varies depending on the source of the data. Access to persistent storage, such as to a database, varies greatly depending on the type of storage (relational databases, object-oriented databases, flat files, and so forth) and the vendor implementation. This DAO generator generate php classes which provide operations on Mysql database
